Class ParameterValueList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yamcs.parameter.ParameterValueList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<ParameterValue>, Collection<ParameterValue>
    public class ParameterValueList
extends Object
implements Collection<ParameterValue>
    Stores a collection of ParameterValue indexed on Parameter It works like a LinkedHashMap<Parameter, LinkedList<ParameterValue>> Not thread safe
